                <h3>üé§ Case Study Presentation (30 points)</h3>
                <p>Identify and define a business problem, propose technical solutions, and make a recommendation. Maximum 15 minutes with voice recording.</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Problem Statement & Overview: 25%</li>
                    <li>Depth of Knowledge/Creativity: 25%</li>
                    <li>Presentation Skills: 25%</li>
                    <li>Participation & Timeliness: 25%</li>
                </ul>

                <h3>üèÜ Final Project (40 points)</h3>
                <p>Individual or group project focused on implementing Web Services and SOA. Includes PowerPoint presentation with voice recording.</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Visual Documentation: 25%</li>
                    <li>Technical Depth: 25%</li>
                    <li>Presentation Skills: 25%</li>
                    <li>Participation & Timeliness: 25%</li>
                </ul>
